headline: These 3 Outstanding Dividend-Growth Stocks Could Fund Your Retirement
summary: Dividend-growth investing remains one of the most reliable paths to building lasting wealth in the stock market.  The appeal of steady, rising income streams is particularly compelling for retirement planning.  After all, traditional fixed-income investments often struggle to keep pace with inflation, making dividend-growth stocks an essential component of a well-designed retirement strategy.
